desc: Whole food, less-processed ingredients. Obsessive quality control. A dramatically different approach to veterinary nutrition. Whether you are treating one or multiple medical conditions, maintaining a healthy pet, raising a puppy or kitten, or trying to find a multi-pet option, Rayne has a diet for that.

layout.text: From Allergies to Urolithiasis and Over Forty Conditions in Between.
Our veterinary diets start with fresh meat and vegetables to deliver the best nutrition to your pet, address existing conditions, and help prevent future ones.
